items.name: Doctor Strange In The Multiverse Of Madness
Warbound
items.description: Hulk is back! As Green Scar, and he will start his revenge against the heroes and the planet that once betrayed him!

items.name: End Of Everything
items.description: He bonded with the primordial symbiote, and even Ego stood no chance against him. He has now becomeLoki the All-Butcher, the End of Everything!

items.name: Rising Dragon
items.description: A recluse sits in tranquility, skies so blue,Amidst amethyst mists, dragons ascend anew.

items.name: Celestial Harmony
items.description: Wearing Vibranium armor, nimble as a breeze, she faces foes with effortless ease. With martial arts and life energy combined, her strength and grace seamlessly align.

items.description: Under divine decree, Marc Spector's journey east unites him with an ancient dragon on the quest to kill a dangerous beast. Together they banish spirits and bathe in moonlight, their reign of peace ever-increasing.

items.name: Cuju Tackler
items.description: After months of training, Doreen can now execute a Cuju tackle with finesse. However, she only achieves a perfect 100% success rate when tackling Tippy-Toe.

items.name: I Am Iron Man
items.description: "Its not about how much we lost, its about how much we have left. Were the Avengers. We gotta finish this."

items.name: Snowflake Catcher
items.description: Catching snowflakes with your tongue isnt just for kidsit's for Symbiotes too!

items.name: No Other Choice
items.description: "I've misplaced clothes before, but losing my Spider-Suit? That's just embarrassing! But you know what they say, crime doesn't wait for you to put your shoes on!"

items.name: Three Generations
items.description: Our friendly neighborhood protectors will save the day again! Here come the Spider-Men!

items.name: Love And Thunder
items.description: I have something worth fighting for, and nothing will hinder Love and Thunder!

items.name: Sun S Out Guns Out
items.description: "You say you are master of the dark? The Void? I'm Master of the Sun."

items.name: Blood Barrage
items.description: The rage of the Wolverine is a force no one can challenge, not even the most menacing blood moon. Newborn monsters cower before the apex predator.

items.name: Lion Dance
items.description: Auspicious lions leap to welcome spring's embrace, Good fortune arrives, bringing joy and grace!
